text: Gareth Low Jun Kit (born 28 February 1997) is a Singaporean who plays as a Midfielder for Hougang United in the S League. ==International career== ===Under-19=== Low was called up and captained the Singapore U19 for the friendlies against Bahrain U19 on 31 August and 3 September 2016. ==International Statistics == === U19 International caps=== {| class="wikitable" !
